  finding: commit 71bf1ee17 "deep-strip(LAMMPS adversary loop)" deleted the entire
    tests/apps/vanillas/LAMMPS/bench/ directory, including bench/in.lj_long, as part of an
    "remove auxiliary trees not built by benchmark" pass. The deletion broke LAMMPS validation
    because tests/apps/configs/LAMMPS.yaml's input_subdir is bench/ and app_args reference
